001230 PROCEDURE DIVISION
	     USING LS-FILE-STATUS LS-FILE LS-KEYX LS-ERROR.
       AA000	       SECTION.
       AA00.
	     MOVE LS-ERROR	 TO WS-IO.
	     MOVE ZERO		 TO LS-ERROR.
	     MOVE LS-FILE-STATUS TO WS-FILE-STATUS
				    W10-STATUS.
	     PERFORM SAVE-SCREEN.
	     PERFORM AA200.
	     EVALUATE WS-STAT1
      * 		  S U C C E S S F U L L
	       WHEN "0"
		       GO TO AA05
      * 		  E N D   O F	F I L E
	       WHEN "1"
		       MOVE 3	 TO LS-ERROR
		       GO TO AA05
      * 		  I N V A L I D   K E Y
	       WHEN "2"
		       PERFORM BA000
      * 		  P E R M A N E N T   E R R O R
	       WHEN "3"
		       PERFORM CA000
      * 		  L O G I C A L   E R R O R
	       WHEN "4"
		       PERFORM DA000
      * 		  R U N   T I M E   S Y S T E M   E R R O R
	       WHEN "9"
		       PERFORM EA000
      * 		  U N I D E N T I F I E D   E R R O R
	       WHEN OTHER
		       PERFORM FA000
	     END-EVALUATE.

       AA05.
	     PERFORM RESTORE-SCREEN.

       AA99.
	     EXIT PROGRAM.
