       AA200	       SECTION 50.
       AA205.
	     MOVE LS-FILE	 TO WS-FILE.
	   IF WS-FILE = SPACES
	       MOVE "NO NAME"	 TO WS-FILE
	       GO TO AA299.
	     MOVE 64		 TO WS-S4.

       AA210.
