	       SUBTRACT 1	 FROM WS-S4
	       GO TO AA210.
	     SUBTRACT 1 FROM WS-S4
				 GIVING WS-S3.

       AA215.
	   IF NOT(WS-FILE-CHAR(WS-S3) = "\") AND
		 (WS-S3 > 1)
	       SUBTRACT 1	 FROM WS-S3
	       GO TO AA215.
	   IF WS-FILE-CHAR(WS-S3) = "\"
	       ADD 1		 TO WS-S3.
	     MOVE SPACES	 TO W05-FILE.
	     MOVE 1		 TO WS-S2.

       AA220.
	     MOVE WS-FILE-CHAR(WS-S3)
				 TO W05-FILE-CHAR(WS-S2).
